(Watsonians); M H McCluskie (Edinburgh Academicals), N R B Dickson
(Boroughmuir), L G A Graham (Boroughmuir), G C Perrett (West of
Scotland), P T Jennings (Boroughmuir), T A McVie (Edinburgh
Academicals), G F Dall (Heriot's FP), capt., D G Clark
(Stewart's-Melville FP).
