<TEXT>
CANON Lewis Smith, of the Scottish Episcopal Church, who is also
convener of Shetland Islands Council, is backing a boycott of Bulgarian
wine in support of striking Bulgarian sailors on board the klondiker
ship Rotalia, stranded in Lerwick. The crew say they have not received
their full wages on board the fish processing ship for three years.
