<TEXT>
TEHRAN: A British Airways jumbo jet flying from New Delhi to London
made an emergency landing at Tehran airport after condensation from
fruit in its cargo hold triggered a fire alarm, a spokesman said. The
plane was carrying 405 passengers and crew from New Delhi to London.
