<TEXT>
TEHRAN: The five wives of a 24-year-old Iranian polygamist confronted
him at the airport as he tried to flee the country. The women had
received an anonymous tip-off by telephone and have filed for divorce,
while the man must stay and settle the case.
</TEXT>
